NB:
networking socket also refers to IP address and port number combo


TCP
reliable
used by HTTP, SMTP, FTP

UDP
unreliable
used by VoIP


Go net Package

func Dial(network, address string) (Conn, error)
opens socket


Write	write to the socket
Read	read from the socket


